<link wikidata="" start="6342" end="6429" title="Black, Blind, &amp;amp; In Charge: A Story of Visionary Leadership and Overcoming Adversity" label="Black, Blind, &amp;amp; In Charge: A Story of Visionary Leadership and Overcoming Adversity"/>
